     "label" -> "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> 
    "QuantumMob/Q3", "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "TheWigner[{j, \\[Mu]}] returns the matrix representation of the angular \
momentum operator J^\\[Mu] of magnitude j in the \\[Mu]^th direction. \
TheWigner[{j, \\[Mu], \\[Theta], \\[Phi]}] returns the matrix representation \
in the rotated frame, U (\\[Theta], \
\\[Phi])\\[CenterDot]J^\\[Mu]\\[CenterDot]U^\\[Dagger] \\ (\\[Theta], \
\\[Phi]). TheWigner[{j1, \\[Mu]1}, {j2, \\[Mu]2}, ...] returns TheWigner[{j1, \
\\[Mu]1}]\\[CircleTimes]TheWigner[{j2, \\[Mu]2\\ }]\\[CircleTimes].... \
TheWigner[{j, {\\[Mu]1, \\[Mu]2, ...}}] is equivalent to TheWigner[{j, \
\\[Mu]1}, {j, \\[Mu]2}, ...}. TheWigner[{J, {k1, k2, ...}, th, ph}] = \
TheWigner[{J, k1, th, ph}, {J, k2, th, ph}, ...].", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "TheWigner", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "TheWigner", "type" -> "Symbol",
     "uri" -> "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/TheWigner"}},
